---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Discordium Investigation">
<main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 space-y-16">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 text-center">

    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6">
      Discordium: Doxxing, Harassment, Predators, Illegal Activity
    </h1>

    <p class="text-xl text-neutral-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      We all know Discord is loaded with predators.  
      But you’d expect that once something serious is exposed… it gets handled.
    </p>

    <p class="text-3xl font-bold mt-10">Wrong.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- INTRO -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-xl">
      <p class="text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
        Discordium.org, operated by Nassvoll (Aljoscha Klemcke), presents itself as a professional Discord advertising platform.
      </p>

      <p class="text-neutral-300 mt-4">
        Evidence suggests something else entirely:
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-6 text-sm">
        <div class="bg-neutral-800 p-3 rounded">Doxxing</div>
        <div class="bg-neutral-800 p-3 rounded">Harassment</div>
        <div class="bg-neutral-800 p-3 rounded">Threats</div>
        <div class="bg-neutral-800 p-3 rounded">Intimidation</div>
        <div class="bg-neutral-800 p-3 rounded">Retaliation</div>
        <div class="bg-neutral-800 p-3 rounded">Predators</div>
        <div class="bg-neutral-800 p-3 rounded">Illegal Activity</div>
        <div class="bg-neutral-800 p-3 rounded">GDPR Violations</div>
        <div class="bg-neutral-800 p-3 rounded">DMCA Violations</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: DOXXING -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Doxxing</h2>

    <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-8">
      Multiple Discordium staff, including leadership, have spread personal information without consent. Sharing PII is a clear violation of Discord TOS.
    </p>

    <!-- IMAGE GRID -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/doxxing-1.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800 md:col-span-2"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/doxxing-2.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800 md:col-span-2"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/doxxing-3.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/doxxing-4.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800 md:col-span-2"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/doxxing-5.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/doxxing-6.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800 md:col-span-2"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/doxxing-7.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/doxxing-8.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
    </div>
    <!-- PUT IMAGES IN: /public/images/doxxing-1.png, doxxing-2.png -->

    <p class="text-neutral-400 mt-6 text-sm">
      Evidence of repeated PII exposure by staff
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: RETALIATION -->
  <section class="bg-neutral-900 border-y border-neutral-800">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">What Happens When You Speak Up?</h2>

      <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-10">
        Instead of accountability, reports are met with dismission, silence—or retaliation.
      </p>

      <!-- IMAGES -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/retaliation-1.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 mt-2">
        Staff issuing legal threats and spreading misleading claims about Discord IDs being “personal data.”
      </p>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/retaliation-14.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/retaliation-2.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/retaliation-3.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/retaliation-4.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/retaliation-5.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/retaliation-6.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/retaliation-7.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/retaliation-8.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/retaliation-9.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/retaliation-10.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/retaliation-11.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/retaliation-12.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800 scale-110"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/retaliation-13.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 mt-2">
Nassvoll publicly insulting users for raising GDPR and privacy concerns.
      </p>
      <!-- /public/images/retaliation-1.png etc -->

      <blockquote class="mt-10 border-l-4 border-red-500 pl-6 text-lg text-neutral-200">
        Threats. Intimidation. Harassment.  
        Both privately and publicly.
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: ESCALATION -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Escalation Instead of Accountability</h2>

    <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-8">
      Evidence shows staff actively attempting to gather more personal data instead of stopping, even going so far as ban evading, another blatant violation of Discord TOS.
    </p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/escalation-1.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
    </div>

  </section>

  <!-- IMPACT BREAK -->
  <section class="text-center py-20 px-6">
    <p class="text-2xl text-neutral-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      No apology. No accountability.
    </p>

    <p class="text-4xl font-bold mt-6">Is this a “professional company”?</p>
  </section>

  <!-- COMMUNITY -->
  <section class="bg-neutral-900 border-y border-neutral-800">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Not Just One Case</h2>

      <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-8">
        This isn't a one-off thing. Similar incidents have been reported by multiple people, over and over.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/community-1.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/community-2.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/community-3.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/community-4.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/community-5.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      </div>

      <blockquote class="mt-10 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 pl-6 text-lg">
        You might all be thinking: This could be fake; or, it could be one hater and multiple alt accounts or friends. And these are valid points. But if the evidence was fake or photoshopped, that would have been Discordium's first statement. And if you look through their responses, you'll realize that they NEVER say this.
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-neutral-900 border-y border-neutral-800">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Review Manipulation</h2>
  
      <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-8">
        After verified negative reviews were mass-reported and removed, Discordium began posting fake positive reviews.
      </p>
  
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/reviews-1.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
        <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/reviews-2.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STAFF ADMISSIONS -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Their Own Staff Confirm It</h2>

    <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-8">
      Internal messages show staff acknowledging misconduct, even gloating about it.
    </p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/staff-1.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/staff-2.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/staff-3.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800 md:col-span-2"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/staff-4.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/staff-5.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/staff-6.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/staff-7.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/staff-8.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/staff-9.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/staff-10.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800 md:col-span-2"/>
      <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 mt-2">
This is a Discordium staff member whom requested their identity be censored due to fear of retaliation.
      </p>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/staff-11.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/staff-12.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800 md:col-span-2"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/staff-13.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 mt-2">
Webhook spam messages sent by a Discordium administrator. A bit extreme, but then again, considering everything Discordium has done, it's rather understandable.
      </p>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/staff-14.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 mt-2">
Nassvoll confirming only administrators had the permissions to send those messages.
      </p>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/staff-15.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 mt-2">
Discordium developer response advising users to “just block” their predators.
      </p>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/staff-16.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 mt-2">
Official response acknowledging misconduct while keeping the same staff in place.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- GDPR -->
  <section class="bg-neutral-900 border-y border-neutral-800">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">GDPR Violations</h2>

      <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-6">
        GDPR is Europe's set of privacy data laws. Article 38 states that the Data Protection Officer (DPO) cannot have a conflict of interest with the controller (Aljoscha Klemcke). But the same individual appears to act as both owner and Data Protection Officer for Discordium.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/gdpr-1.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/gdpr-2.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      </div>

      <p class="text-neutral-400 mt-6">
        Policy changes were made without notice after being questioned. Now, they don't have a DPO listed at all, despite collecting personal data such as emails and legal names. 
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DMCA -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">DMCA & Copyright Issues</h2>

    <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-8">
      Discordium lists bots they do not own and claim to be the bot developers. A lot of well-known bots, such as Poketwo, Mudae, Tatsumaki, Carl, and others were included.
    </p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/bot-1.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/bot-2.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/bot-3.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/bot-4.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/bot-5.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/bot-6.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/bot-7.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/bot-8.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/bot-9.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/bot-10.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/bot-11.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/bot-12.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
    </div>
    <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-8">
      Their staff have also had DMCA violations and takedowns issued against them. 
    </p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/dmca-1.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/dmca-2.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-neutral-900 border-y border-neutral-800">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Recognized Beyond Discord</h2>
  
      <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-8">
        Multiple communities, websites, and organizations have banned or blacklisted Discordium. This isn't "just Discord drama."
      </p>
  
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/external-1.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
        <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/external-2.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
        <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/external-3.png`} class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800"/>
        <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-8">
      Discordium bans people who ban their staff in retaliation. 
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- FINAL -->
  <section class="text-center py-24 px-6">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
      Harassment. Doxxing. Threats. Predators.
    </h2>

    <p class="text-neutral-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
      Reported repeatedly. Documented extensively. Still active.
    </p>

    <p class="text-2xl font-semibold">
      What are you going to do about it?
    </p>
  </section>

</main>
</BaseLayout>
